		<div id="story-body" class="story-body">

			<div class="lede-container">
<figure id="media-100000006161597" class="media photo lede layout-large-horizontal ratio-tall" data-media-action="modal" itemprop="associatedMedia" itemscope itemid="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2018/10/17/world/europe/17brexit-hoarding-1-print/16Prepper1-master1050.jpg" itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" aria-label="media" role="group">
	<a class="visually-hidden skip-to-text-link" href="#story-continues-2">Continue reading the main story</a>	<span class="visually-hidden">Foto</span>
	<div class="image">
		<img src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2018/10/17/world/europe/17brexit-hoarding-1-print/16Prepper1-master1050.jpg" alt="" class="media-viewer-candidate" data-mediaviewer-src="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2018/10/17/world/europe/17brexit-hoarding-1-print/16Prepper1-superJumbo.jpg" data-mediaviewer-caption="Nevine y Richard Mann han comenzado a plantar cultivos en su jardín en Cornualles, Inglaterra, en caso de que el brexit interrumpa el suministro de alimentos." data-mediaviewer-credit="James Beck para The New York Times"  itemprop="url" itemid="https://static01.nyt.com/images/2018/10/17/world/europe/17brexit-hoarding-1-print/16Prepper1-master1050.jpg"/>
		<meta itemprop="height" content="700" />
		<meta itemprop="width" content="1050" />
	</div>
	<figcaption class="caption" itemprop="caption description">
		<span class="caption-text">Nevine y Richard Mann han comenzado a plantar cultivos en su jardín en Cornualles, Inglaterra, en caso de que el brexit interrumpa el suministro de alimentos.</span>
		<span class="credit" itemprop="copyrightHolder">
			<span class="visually-hidden">Credit</span>
			James Beck para The New York Times
		</span>
	</figcaption>
</figure>
	<!--<div class="lede-container-ads">
		<div id="lede-ad" class="ad lede-ad marginalia-anchor-ad nocontent robots-nocontent">
